<font color="#FF0000">CIVIL RIGHTS IN VIETNAM?</font><br>
<tt>Thu Nov 13  9:10:43 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Another interesting story on present day Vietnam<br><br>
Chirac talks human rights in Vietnam <br>
 <br>
French president begins five-day visit to former colony <br>
 <br>
REUTER <br>
 <br>
HANOI, Vietnam — French President Jacques Chirac broached the thorny issue of human rights with his Vietnamese counterpart on Wednesday, just hours after arriving for a five-day visit aimed at boosting bilateral relations between France and Vietnam. <br>
 <br>
